<li><a class="newpage" href="#">SCP-2634</a> (&quot;A Higher Power&quot;) - Life exists in far stranger places than we can conceive of. And it is reaching out to us. Written by Dr Solo.</li>
<li><a class="newpage" href="#">SCP-2891</a> (&quot;Insta-Container!&quot;) - You can't stop the world from changing - but you can seal yourself away from it. Contained by BananaRepublic.</li>
