<li><a class="newpage" href="#">SCP-2541</a> (&quot; Ecological Anomaly of Midassia&quot;) - And God said, &quot;Let the land produce living creatures according to their kinds: the livestock, the creatures that move along the ground, and the wild animals, each according to its kind.&quot; And it was so. Written by Moenennbys.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc8"><span>Tales:</span></h4>
